The messages should be archived before deleted. Only received messages can be deleted, the sent messages are kept to verify the origin via ilhapush.

1.Click on the “messages” button;

2.Select the box beside the messages that you want to delete;

3.When selected, click on the “Archived” folder located on your inbox;

4.Click on the “Archived” folder located on the left of your messages. Select messages that you want to delete. When verified, click on the trash (icon located on the top of the list).
